{"tid":1596584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"929台灣前哨戰！！好重要","createTime":"2019-09-26T14:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T17:06:56.000Z","uid":215547,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3e88c9dbdfc10782ed8481e45346888ef0ac1b0a","tid":1596584,"uid":215547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGTpG56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGTpG56.jpg&h=1eafbd4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我相信呢個暑假,好多人發過好多場夢,無奈既係要離港讀書。<br />\n但台灣戰線已經開始緊!!有手足被大陸人攻擊!! 在台港人一定要團結,一日未到除罩相認,呢場夢都未完。<br />\n<br />\n929一定要吹大雞! 證明我地唔會置身事外,將香港人團結精神蔓延至台灣!<br />\n<br />\n加上台灣既反共意識都好接近我地, 呢次一定要成功connect!!<br />\n<br />\n歡迎入黎@taiwanantichinazi  支持在台港人既戰線。<br />\n唔只要遍地開花, 係要遍國開花!!!<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命!<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qei5rxS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQei5rxS.jpg&h=72ce86f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NWAb6xW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNWAb6xW.jpg&h=796e9a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/26/222108_dbaf7d275c03b1d22d7350e01fccf54d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F26%2F222108_dbaf7d275c03b1d22d7350e01fccf54d.jpg&h=c2566508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nxpz4oK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxpz4oK.jpg&h=9199804f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0ZoXJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0ZoXJL.jpg&h=4b643c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9cq7EW6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9cq7EW6.jpg&h=70bb9019&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C25C2as.jpg\" data-